# Input Mapping Context for One Piece Wano Game
# This file represents the default input mapping context
# In a real project, this would be created in the Unreal Editor as a .uasset file

# Movement Controls:
# - WASD: Move character
# - Mouse: Look around
# - Space: Jump
# - Left Mouse: Basic Attack
# - Right Mouse: Special Attack (Devil Fruit)
# - Q: Activate Haki
# - E: Interact
# - Tab: Character Switch (if available)
# - Esc: Pause Menu